{"tid":2350314,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"2款折疊式 iPhone 通過 Apple 耐用性測試，推出只係時間問題","createTime":"2021-01-02T08:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T14:10:59.000Z","uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"330c35ed26982ded9be103f64eef4db0dde83a48","tid":2350314,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:10:59.000Z","msg":"根據科技情報網站 Economic Daily News 的消息指出，目前已經有 2 款折疊式 iPhone 原型機通過了 Apple 內部的耐用性測試。<br />\n<br />\n        報導表示，Apple 設計了兩款不同折疊式 iPhone 系統，它們最近在中國深圳的 Foxconn 工廠完成。<br />\n<br />\n        第一款經過測試的可折疊 iPhone 是雙螢幕款式，這很可能是 Jon Prosser 於 2020 年 6 月曝光的原型，Jon Prosser 當時便稱儘管這個折疊式 iPhone 擁有兩個螢幕，但是他們看起來完全連續的，堪稱無縫連接。此外，值得注意的是 Apple 早已為該設備申請專利，它具有兩個獨立的螢幕，並透過一個帶有鉸鏈的佈建讓他們組合在一起。<br />\n<br />\n        第二個通過測試的原型是翻蓋式的可折疊 iPhone，較類似於 Samsung Galaxy Z Flip，該翻蓋模型設置為先前 Apple 大量訂購的 Samsung OLED 顯示器。"},{"pid":"d1ebd1dc7e13600d5250177f7b6911918edceb93","tid":2350314,"uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"iFold &amp; iFlip<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecOLNFQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecOLNFQ.png&h=b9b6f67d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jypSsFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjypSsFQ.jpg&h=da591a99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9501cecb179d6f0d6ca34f23725ede5c21f42262","tid":2350314,"uid":140335,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"個mon摺爛左 : 用家問題"},{"pid":"367ccb719ce30878325e35a42f97bc5eaa7a8c5a","tid":2350314,"uid":31098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9501cecb179d6f0d6ca34f23725ede5c21f42262","tid":2350314,"uid":140335,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"個mon摺爛左 : 用家問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"You fold the phone wrong <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"